<p align="center" style="text-align:center; text-indent:-.75pt"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="line-height:normal"><span style="tab-stops:56.65pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:Palatino">TMP-SMX DS 1-2 tabs BID + cephalexin 500 QID OR Amoxicillin-clavulanate 875/125 BID</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p align="center" style="text-align:center; text-indent:-.75pt"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="line-height:normal"><span style="tab-stops:56.65pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:Palatino">Vancomycin 15-20mg/kg q8-12h + ampicillin-sulbactam 3g q6h (anaerobic but NO Pseudomonas cvg*) OR cefepime 2g</span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:Palatino"> q8h (<i>Pseudomonas</i> cvg) + metronidazole 500 q8h (anaerobic cvg)</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
